HEADWORD: Dabbler
<hw>Dab"bler</hw> <pr>(d⟦acr⟧b"bl⟦etil⟧r)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<sn>1.</sn> <def>One who dabbles.</def>⟦br⟧
